"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran has published a map claiming control over more than 22,000 square kilometers of a waterway. This move shows Iran's assertion of power in the region.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Claims Waterway\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ir\u00e1n ha publicado un mapa diciendo que controla m\u00e1s de 22,000 kil\u00f3metros cuadrados de un canal de agua. Esto muestra el poder de Ir\u00e1n en la regi\u00f3n.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n dice que controla canal\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A video has surfaced showing a far-right Israeli minister mocking activists who were kneeling with their hands tied. This video has been condemned by many people.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Minister Mocks Activists\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un video muestra a un ministro de Israel burl\u00e1ndose de activistas que estaban arrodillados con las manos atadas. Muchas personas han criticado este video.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ministro de Israel se burla de activistas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Sexually transmitted infections have increased due to record cases and gaps in testing and prevention, according to a health agency report.\",            \"english_title\": \"Increase in Infections\",            \"translated_version\": \"Las infecciones de transmisi\u00f3n sexual han aumentado por casos r\u00e9cord y falta de pruebas y prevenci\u00f3n, seg\u00fan un informe de salud.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Aumento de infecciones\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A blockade has caused shortages of fuel and food just before the Muslim holiday of Eid. This situation is causing concern among the people affected.\",            \"english_title\": \"Blockade Causes Shortages\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un bloqueo ha causado falta de combustible y comida justo antes de la fiesta musulmana de Eid. Esta situaci\u00f3n preocupa a las personas afectadas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Bloqueo causa escasez\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A rare Ebola outbreak is believed to have caused 139 deaths so far. The World Health Organization reports there have been 139 suspected deaths and 600 cases.\",            \"english_title\": \"Ebola Outbreak\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un raro brote de \u00c9bola ha causado 139 muertes hasta ahora. La Organizaci\u00f3n Mundial de la Salud dice que hay 139 muertes sospechosas y 600 casos.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Brote de \u00c9bola\"        }    ]}"